01:24:19.199 --> 01:24:20.720
Originalmente te apellidabas Xue.

01:24:21.079 --> 01:24:22.800
No soy Lu Zhi.

01:24:32.560 --> 01:24:34.239
No soy Lu Buyou.

01:24:39.840 --> 01:24:40.640
Tú...

01:24:43.000 --> 01:24:44.600
¿No eres Lu Buyou?

01:24:45.560 --> 01:24:48.159
¿Aún recuerdas a Xiaobao?

01:24:49.159 --> 01:24:50.479
Xiaobao.

01:24:53.760 --> 01:24:54.680
